  "name": "TrustM365",
  "description": "TrustM365 is a free, self-hosted dashboard for Microsoft 365 administrators and MSSPs. It connects to multiple tenants via Graph, baselines exact resources and properties to monitor, detects drift with property-level diffs on every sync, and restores baseline values with one click. It provides branded reports, webhook alerts, and a full audit trail, plus auto-restore and multi-tenant views for MSSP workflows.",
